			<img class="card-img-top" src="images/oxala.jpg" alt="Card image cap">
				<h2 class="card-title"><center>OXALÁ</center></h2>
					<p class="card-text">
			

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><strong><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">OXAL&Aacute; </span></span></strong></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">A palavra Oxal&aacute; significa &ldquo;O Grande Orix&aacute;&rdquo; ou ainda &ldquo;Senhor da Luz Divina&rdquo;. Alguns escritores dizem que os negros escravos se referiam a Oxal&aacute; pelo nome Orixal&aacute;, que significa Orix&aacute; dos Orix&aacute;s, e por contra&ccedil;&atilde;o o termo Orixal&aacute;, passou a ser simplesmente Oxal&aacute;. Em locais da &Aacute;frica era conhecido como <strong>Obatal&aacute;</strong>, que vem a ser o Oxal&aacute; original. </span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Considerado tamb&eacute;m o Grande Pai, por ser o mais velho de todos os Orix&aacute;s e por ser pai de todos os Orix&aacute;s e de todos os seres do c&eacute;u e da terra. &Eacute; a concep&ccedil;&atilde;o no sentido masculino do termo. Apesar do t&iacute;tulo de pai dos Orix&aacute;s, &eacute; sabido que nem Iemanj&aacute; e nem Loguned&eacute; s&atilde;o seus filhos. </span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Segundo a defini&ccedil;&atilde;o de Z&eacute;lio de Moraes, mostrado por Ronaldo Antonio Linares, Oxal&aacute; seria aquele que traz o poder total de Deus dentro de si, que foi dividido aos seus filhos Orix&aacute;s. Por este motivo cada Orix&aacute; tem a sua cor, e a de Oxal&aacute; &eacute; o branco, que &eacute; a soma de todas as cores. </span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Na &Aacute;frica era o mais respeitado entre os Orix&aacute;s <em>Fun-Fun</em> (Orix&aacute;s Brancos) e tamb&eacute;m atribu&iacute;am a ele a cria&ccedil;&atilde;o da Terra, apesar de algumas lendas questionarem este ponto. Contudo, Oxal&aacute; &eacute; aquele que atua sobre as pessoas o tempo todo, a mais elevada energia divina. </span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Oxal&aacute; atua em todos os campos, por&eacute;m &eacute; na f&eacute; e na religiosidade das pessoas que se encontra seu ponto mais proeminente. &Eacute; ele que conecta os esp&iacute;ritos dos encarnados com o Orun, o c&eacute;u ou plano espiritual o tempo todo. Por este motivo o chacra que o rege &eacute; coron&aacute;rio (alto da cabe&ccedil;a) e &eacute; por ele que Oxal&aacute; aplica a sua mais pura vibra&ccedil;&atilde;o em todos os seres. Resumindo, Oxal&aacute; &eacute; elo que nos conecta a Olorun (Deus). </span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Afastar-se de Oxal&aacute; &eacute; afastar-se de Deus, das virtudes, e, dessa forma, tornar-se presa f&aacute;cil para a espiritualidade inferior. </span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">O Candombl&eacute; influ&ecirc;ncia algumas casa de Umbanda, pois dividem o culto de Oxal&aacute; em outros dois: Oxagui&atilde;, Oxal&aacute; mo&ccedil;o e guerreiro, cujo s&iacute;mbolo &eacute; o id&aacute; (espada) e Oxaluf&atilde;, Oxal&aacute; velho e s&aacute;bio, j&aacute; arcado pelo tempo, sempre apoiado em seu opaxor&ocirc; (cajado). Oxaluf&atilde; simboliza muito a imagem que a maioria dos umbandistas tem de Oxal&aacute;. </span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Por ser o detentor primeiro do poder de Deus, possui de forma globalizada, o conhecimento e o poder de todos os outros Orix&aacute;s. Muito se diz que se n&atilde;o souber a quem pedir, pe&ccedil;a a Oxal&aacute; por este motivo. </span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">A palavra que simboliza Oxal&aacute; &eacute; a f&eacute;. &Eacute; pela f&eacute; que chegamos a ele e podemos usufruir de suas b&ecirc;n&ccedil;&atilde;os. </span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify">&nbsp;</p>

<ul>
	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><strong><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">O que pedir?</span></span></strong></span></span></span></li>
</ul>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Recorremos a Oxal&aacute; quando precisamos nos aproximar do Sagrado, do Divino; para firmar nossa cabe&ccedil;a e despertar nossa f&eacute;, em casos de situa&ccedil;&otilde;es extremamente complexas de resolver, para a b&ecirc;n&ccedil;&atilde;o de pais encarnados, para trazer uma pessoa ou situa&ccedil;&atilde;o para a luz.</span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Por &uacute;ltimo e mais importante, a maior b&ecirc;n&ccedil;&atilde;o que Oxal&aacute; pode nos outorgar &eacute; a paz, e tamb&eacute;m &eacute; constantemente solicitado para dissolver conflitos ou diferen&ccedil;as de qualquer tipo. </span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify">&nbsp;</p>

<ul>
	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><strong><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Caracter&iacute;sticas de Oxal&aacute; e seus filhos </span></span></strong></span></span></span></li>
</ul>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Oxal&aacute; tem temperamento ao mesmo tempo calmo e d&oacute;cil, por&eacute;m determinado. &Eacute; alheio a qualquer tipo de viol&ecirc;ncia, briga ou disputa, por&eacute;m gosta da autoridade e da hierarquia. &Eacute; extremamente afeito &agrave; ordem, &agrave; limpeza e &agrave; pureza. </span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">S&atilde;o conselheiros por natureza. S&atilde;o ambiciosos e podem se dar muito bem no com&eacute;rcio e nas finan&ccedil;as, e mesmo em atividades ligadas &agrave; ci&ecirc;ncia como professor, escritor, qu&iacute;mico e projetista. </span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">S&atilde;o fechados e dificilmente se abrem totalmente com algu&eacute;m. S&atilde;o sens&iacute;veis, inflex&iacute;veis e extremamente inteligentes. </span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Pelo tipo de personalidade normalmente recebem muitas ingratid&otilde;es, e o maior desejo de Oxal&aacute; &eacute; ser reconhecido. </span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Os filhos de Oxal&aacute; podem ter problemas de calv&iacute;cie e vis&atilde;o. </span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">S&atilde;o perfeccionistas, carinhosos, ligados &agrave; fam&iacute;lia, s&atilde;o excelentes pais ou m&atilde;es. Bondosos, altru&iacute;stas, liberais. S&atilde;o a autoridade em pessoa. Por&eacute;m, em desequil&iacute;brio, s&atilde;o invejosos, excessivamente vaidosos, maledicentes, autorit&aacute;rios, confusos, hipocondr&iacute;acos e temperamentais. </span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Quando equilibrados s&atilde;o lentos, am&aacute;veis e sens&iacute;veis, e qualquer desequil&iacute;brio pode afetar seriamente sua sa&uacute;de. </span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Tranquilos, vivem afastados do mundo real, sendo pouco propensos &agrave;s paix&otilde;es, aos instintos carnais e &agrave;s coisas materiais. </span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Grande for&ccedil;a moral, &iacute;ntegros, tem plena consci&ecirc;ncia de sua intelig&ecirc;ncia e de seu valor. N&atilde;o gostam de trair ou mentir, e quando o fazem, n&atilde;o a sustentam por muito tempo. Generosos e tolerantes, adoram crian&ccedil;as e n&atilde;o gostam de se afastar delas. </span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">S&atilde;o l&iacute;deres naturais e assumem postos de comando facilmente em qualquer local ou ocasi&atilde;o. </span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Apesar de contradit&oacute;rio, &eacute; nos filhos de Oxal&aacute; que a vaidade melhor pode ser percebida. Gostam de se vestir bem e s&atilde;o extremamente agrad&aacute;veis. Com as mulheres s&atilde;o compreensivos e rom&acirc;nticos. Com todas essas qualidades n&atilde;o &eacute; de se estranhar que o filho de Oxal&aacute; chame tanto a aten&ccedil;&atilde;o das mulheres. </span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">A filha de Oxal&aacute; &eacute; m&atilde;e dedicada e esposa perfeita para qualquer homem, pois se preocupa com a casa e com a fam&iacute;lia. &Eacute; t&iacute;mida, discreta, e tamb&eacute;m direta e sincera. Veste-se bem, por&eacute;m com discri&ccedil;&atilde;o. Tamb&eacute;m chama a aten&ccedil;&atilde;o dos homens, por&eacute;m s&oacute; se interessa pelos gentis, inteligentes e cavalheiros. </span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">O homem que conquistar uma filha de Oxal&aacute; pode se surpreender com sua sensualidade, o que ela s&oacute; far&aacute; quando estiver certa de si mesma. </span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify">&nbsp;</p>

<ul>
	<li style="text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><strong><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Outros Detalhes</span></span></strong></span></span></span></li>
</ul>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Sincretismo: Jesus Cristo;</span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Data de culto: 25 de Dezembro;</span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Sauda&ccedil;&atilde;o: Epa Bab&aacute; (Salve o Pai, com admira&ccedil;&atilde;o),ou Bab&aacute; Ok&ecirc; (Salve o Pai) ou Ex&ecirc; Uep&ecirc; Bab&aacute; (Oxal&aacute; &eacute; meu Pai); </span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">&Aacute;rea de atua&ccedil;&atilde;o: A paz, a f&eacute;, o progresso e sa&uacute;de;</span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Elemento: Ar e &eacute;ter;</span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Chacra: Coron&aacute;rio;</span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Metal: Ouro branco, prata e platina;</span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Astro regente: Sol;</span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Dia da semana: Domingo;</span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Cor da guia: Branca leitosa;</span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Cor da vela: Branca;</span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Pedra: Diamante ou cristal;</span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Bebida: Suco de uva, &aacute;gua e vinho doce;</span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Amal&aacute;: Milho branco, arroz com mel, canjica doce; </span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Frutas: Uva verde, pera, damasco, figo, polpa de coco, p&ecirc;ssego;</span></span></span></span></span></p>

<p style="margin-left:0cm; margin-right:0cm; text-align:justify"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="color:black"><span style="font-size:14.0pt"><span style="font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Flores: Girassol, l&iacute;rio branco e todas as flores brancas (rosas sem espinhos);</span></span></span></span></span></p>

